<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ACT 4 - Audio and Image</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --sour-lavender: #b19cd9;
            --sour-dark-bg: #0d0b14; 
            --sour-card-bg: #1a1625; 
        }
        body {
            margin: 0;
            background-color: var(--sour-dark-bg);
            font-family: sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .audio-page {
            min-height: 100vh; 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center; 
            padding-top: 60px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .scroll-text {
            background: var(--sour-lavender); 
            color: var(--sour-dark-bg); 
            padding: 15px 0; 
            font-size: 24px; 
            font-weight: 900; 
            width: 100%;
            white-space: nowrap; 
            animation: scrolling 25s linear infinite;
            text-transform: uppercase; 
            letter-spacing: 2px; 
            position: absolute; 
            top: 10%;
        }
        @keyframes scrolling { 
            0% { transform: translateX(100%); } 
            100% { transform: translateX(-100%); } 
        }
        
        .album-art {
            width: 350px; 
            border: 12px solid white; 
            border-bottom: 60px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.7); 
            transform: rotate(-2deg); 
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .audio-box { 
            background: var(--sour-card-bg); 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 20px; 
            border: 2px solid var(--sour-lavender); 
            text-align: center;
        }
        .soft2-title { 
            color: var(--sour-lavender); 
            margin-bottom: 15px; 
            font-size: 22px; 
            font-weight: 800; 
        }
        audio {
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="audio-page">
        <div class="scroll-text"> SOUR • good 4 u • traitor • drivers license • deja vu </div>
        
        <img src="sour_cover.jpg" alt="SOUR Album Art" class="album-art">
        
        <div class="audio-box">
            <h2 class="soft2-title">Now Playing: good 4 u</h2>
            <audio controls>
                <source src="good4u.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
                Your browser does not support the audio element.
            </audio>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
